---
layout: layouts/page.njk
permalink: /tags/
title: Tags
---
<section>
  <h1>Browse by tag</h1>
  <p class="section-intro">A quick map of recurring topics. Tags exclude the internal <code>posts</code> helper.</p>
</section>

{% set tagEntries = collections.combinedTagEntries %}
<ul class="tags-grid">
  {% for entry in tagEntries %}
    <li>
      <a href="/tags/{{ entry.slug }}/">{{ entry.name }} <span class="post-meta">({{ entry.items | length }})</span></a>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
